Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.97,0:22:59.34,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Gordon and Grey's Comedy Routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:23:00.06,top,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,G-G-G-Gordon and Grey's Comedy Routine!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.06,0:23:04.32,sign_33089_334_Bulls,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Bulls
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.08,0:23:04.32,sign_33137_335_Hello__we_re_Gor,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Hello, we're Gordon and Grey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.13,0:23:08.45,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.45,0:23:11.93,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Don't listen to my voice, either!\N Cover your ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.93,0:23:15.20,sign_33137_335_Hello__we_re_Gor,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}But then we can't do our comedy routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:20.14,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I can't tell what \Nyou're saying anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.14,0:23:22.07,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,so how can we even do a comedy routine?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.85,0:23:25.69,sign_33137_335_Hello__we_re_Gor,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Well, you got me there. Hahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:30.66,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's all from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:38.35,sign_33089_334_Bulls,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1935)}Bulls
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:37.14,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You two need to apologize \Nto every comedian out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.10,0:23:42.48,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What? What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:45.50,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are, \Nbut speak faster, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.50,0:23:48.61,main,gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, \NPage 90: "Crazy Magic Battle."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 90\N\N{\fs18} Crazy Magic Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:50.82,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,My little sister, the goddess Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:54.03,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna hurry up and end this \Nbattle so I can come see you!
